    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/5a724f11b34fbc287b22d512813a3f9d.avif?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=392 /></span><br>故事发生在大都会之国，当国家陷入经济危机时，你挺身而出成为展会主办方，打算通过漫展拯救世界。<br>游戏的终极目标是打败其他竞争对手，成为漫展之王。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/3f1d30c6ab8fd7fddbfb1608b295963e.poster.avif?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/3f1d30c6ab8fd7fddbfb1608b295963e.webm?t=1771087549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/3f1d30c6ab8fd7fddbfb1608b295963e.mp4?t=1771087549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/7e27fadcb0fcd2834fbc1674a259a961.webp?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搭建你的个性漫展</h2>扮演身份与能力各异的主办方筹办一轮轮漫展，自由安排并合理规划摊位和NPC满足观众的需求。在SLG模式下，你还需要利用技能卡牌打败其它主办方。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/d723265e44c586cc08c8d036b3797a38.avif?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=130 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >应对随机事件并发掘彩蛋</h2>火灾？丧尸？外星人？种种脑洞大开的随机事件和精心准备的彩蛋，让你在游戏中体验更多意料之外的乐趣！ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/a69ab19d6c3b7d2060621831410877e8.avif?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=130 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对MOD的完善支持</h2>通过简单的步骤，你就能制作并导入你设计的摊位/角色/NPC。游戏也完整支持创意工坊，欢迎大家在创意工坊和社区里分享自己的创意哟！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917020/extras/28e391133b0b9a9a87a29ce93a0b0366.avif?t=1771087549\" width=616 height=130 /></span>",
